model.datastore.mysql

Class CustomerDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.datastore.mysql.CustomerDAO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICustomerDAO

    public class CustomerDAO
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICustomerDAO
    The "CustomerDAO" (Data Access Object) class handles all the interactions with the data store. This version uses a MySQL database to store the data. It is multi-user safe.
